Why I Support Planned Parenthood⁣
⁣
Our country and our rights are at a pivotal moment.⁣
⁣
Judge Amy Coney Barret is dangerously close to a lifetime appointment on the Supreme Court.⁣
⁣
She is a direct threat to reproductive freedom and birth control, and if confirmed, she will hear a case on the Affordable Care Act just one week after the election that could cause more than 60 MILLION people to lose access to birth control coverage with no out-of pocket costs.⁣
 ⁣
This is our moment to rise up.⁣
⁣
We must #AllRise for justice and protect the people’s seat, our right for reproductive freedom, and our right to birth control.⁣
⁣
We must tell our U.S. senators that there should be no confirmation until after the 2021 inauguration.⁣
⁣
